    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🌐 Network Ops AI Agent\n### Meraki + ThousandEyes\n\n**How it works:**\n1. User sends a chat message\n2. AI Agent processes it using the system prompt\n3. Agent calls Meraki and/or ThousandEyes MCP tools as needed\n4. Response is returned to the chat\n\n---\n\n**Example questions to ask:**\n- \"What clients are connected to my network?\"\n- \"Show me firmware versions for all devices\"\n- \"Are there any ThousandEyes alerts?\"\n- \"Troubleshoot the device with hostname <<>>\"\n- \"What are my recent config changes?\"",
        "height": 736,
        "width": 320,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "bc761a25-f5e4-4f8b-91aa-06a280967f97",
      "name": "Setup Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1536,
        112
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
          "mode": "list",
          "cachedResultName": "Claude Haiku 4.5"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatAnthropic",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        -1136,
        464
      ],
      "id": "e1542133-623d-4bc1-8dfa-f8a59d54f01f",
