    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ThousandEyes \nMCP Client\n\n\n\n\n\n\nThe ThousandEyes MCP Server provides access to your enterprise's ThousandEyes data:\n\n* **Core Monitoring**\n  _Get details on test, events, alerts, and outages_\n\n* **Endpoint Monitoring​ nad Network Path Analysis**\n _Get endpoint agent tests and metrics and perform network path analysis_ \n\n* **Advanced Analysis**\n  _Get anomalies and metrics_ \n\n\nhttps://docs.thousandeyes.com/product-documentation/integration-guides/thousandeyes-mcp-server\n\n\n\n\n\n",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -304,
        384
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "0006a2e4-700b-481c-8418-9746cc6f32c7",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## LLM Model\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nThe LLM will adopt the persona specified in the system prompt, interpret user messages, determine which MCP tools are needed to gather data, and provide the response. \n\nCan be a cloud service (Claude, GPT, Gemini, etc) or hosted on-prem on a GPU running a local model. \n\n\n\n\n",
        "height": 464,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -1200,
        384
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "8d22b411-c073-4724-a7b3-d24fad8fe752",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Memory\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAllows agent to store the last few messages in memory to stay on topic. Larger memory allows for longer connected conversations but will consume more tokens. \n\n\n\n",
        "height": 464,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -752,
        384
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "8f6753a5-f0c3-4106-a6fa-65eb86638976",
      "name": "Sticky Note5"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Meraki\nMCP Client\n\n\n\n\n\n\nThe Meraki MCP Server provides access to your enterprise's Meraki environment data:\n\nThe entire Meraki API of nearly 900 endpoints is available as tools. \n\n\n\n\nThis demo uses Selent-AI's open sourced Meraki MCP wrapper: https://github.com/selent-ai/selent-mcp \n\n",
        "height": 464,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
